  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Retail Sales Executive",
  "description": "<p>Looking for a people-focused role that builds confidence, communication skills, and real earning potential without the crazy 12-hour retail shifts? Join Superstar Teacher as a Retail Sales Executive and gain hands-on experience while growing with a supportive, energetic team!</p><p><strong>What’s In It for You</strong></p><ul><li>Gross salary from $2,800/month <em>(Base + attractive commission)</em></li><li>Performance cash incentives to reward your hustle</li><li>Better work-life balance with 5-day work week, 12pm to 8pm</li><li>Birthday leave + medical benefits</li></ul><p><strong>What You’ll Do:</strong></p><ul><li>Be our brand ambassador at booth locations within retail malls</li><li>Approach and engage customers in a friendly and professional way</li><li>Demonstrate and explain product features and promotions with confidence</li><li>Guide customers to make the right purchase decision</li><li>Keep the booth looking sharp and materials tidy</li></ul><p><strong>Who We’re Looking For</strong></p><ul><li>Min. O-Level qualification</li><li>Retail / event promo experience is a plus</li><li>Able to converse in Mandarin</li><li>Willing to work retail hours, including weekends and public holidays</li></ul><p><em>If you're outgoing, self-motivated and ready to grow with a team that values your energy and potential; we’d love to meet you.</em></p>",
